---

<Layout
  title="MLB チーム一覧 | 全30球団 地区別データ | Baseballab"
  description="MLB全30球団をア・リーグ／ナ・リーグ地区別に一覧。各球団の成績データ・所属選手情報を掲載。"
  ogUrl="https://baseballab.com/teams/"
>
  <style slot="head">
    .teams-hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 60%, #1a5276 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem 2.75rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .teams-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(192,57,43,.85);
      font-size: .75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: .3rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .teams-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.5vw, 2.75rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
      margin-bottom: .85rem;
    }
    .teams-hero h1 em { color: #7ec8e3; font-style: normal; }
    .teams-sub {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-size: clamp(.9rem, 1.8vw, 1.02rem);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .breadcrumb {
      padding: .75rem 0;
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: var(--gray-500);
    }
    .breadcrumb a { color: var(--gray-500); }
    .breadcrumb span { margin: 0 .4rem; }
    .section { padding: 3rem 0; }
    .section-alt { background: var(--gray-100); }
    .league-label {
      display: inline-block;
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: .75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: .4rem;
    }
    .league-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--navy);
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .div-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .div-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .div-head {
      padding: .6rem 1.1rem;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--navy);
    }
    .team-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
      padding: .75rem 1.1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
      color: inherit;
      transition: background .15s;
    }
    .team-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .team-row:hover { background: #f0f4f8; }
    .team-dot {
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
    }
    .team-abbr {
      font-size: .75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--gray-400);
      width: 2.8rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-variant: small-caps;
    }
    .team-name {
      flex: 1;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--navy-dark);
      font-size: .9rem;
    }
    .team-arrow { color: var(--gray-300); font-size: 1rem; }
    .team-row:hover .team-arrow { color: var(--red); }
    .npb-banner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9b2335 0%, #7d1c2a 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.4rem 1.75rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .npb-banner:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .npb-banner-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
    .npb-banner-body { flex: 1; }
    .npb-banner-title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: .2rem; }
    .npb-banner-sub { font-size: .85rem; opacity: .8; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .div-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>

  <section class="teams-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="teams-eyebrow">⚾ MLB Teams</p>
      <h1>MLB 全<em>30</em>球団</h1>
      <p class="teams-sub">アメリカン・リーグ／ナショナル・リーグ 各地区の球団データ。選手成績・チーム分析を掲載。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">トップ</a><span>›</span><span>チーム一覧</span>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <!-- AL -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="league-label">American League</p>
      <h2 class="league-title">アメリカン・リーグ</h2>
      <div class="div-grid">
        {AL.map(({ div, teams }) => (
          <div class="div-card">
            <div class="div-head">{div}</div>
            {teams.map(t => (
              <a href={`/teams/${t.slug}/`} class="team-row">
                <span class="team-dot" style={`background:${t.color}`}></span>
                <span class="team-abbr">{t.abbr}</span>
                <span class="team-name">{t.name}</span>
                <span class="team-arrow">›</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NL -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="league-label">National League</p>
      <h2 class="league-title">ナショナル・リーグ</h2>
      <div class="div-grid">
        {NL.map(({ div, teams }) => (
          <div class="div-card">
            <div class="div-head">{div}</div>
            {teams.map(t => (
              <a href={`/teams/${t.slug}/`} class="team-row">
                <span class="team-dot" style={`background:${t.color}`}></span>
                <span class="team-abbr">{t.abbr}</span>
                <span class="team-name">{t.name}</span>
                <span class="team-arrow">›</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <a href="/npb/" class="npb-banner">
        <div class="npb-banner-icon">🇯🇵</div>
        <div class="npb-banner-body">
          <div class="npb-banner-title">NPBデータはこちら — セ・パ12球団</div>
          <div class="npb-banner-sub">2026シーズン最新成績・選手データを毎日更新中</div>
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:1.4rem;opacity:.7">→</div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
